props.name: text
props.description: Text to use within the back link component. If content is provided in the default slot, this prop will be ignored.

props.name: href
props.description: The value of the link's `href` attribute.

props.name: component
props.description: The component used to render the link, for example `RouterLink`.

slots.name: default
slots.description: The content of the back link. If content is provided in this slot, the `text` prop will be ignored.
